To install simple move the .pl file to ~/.config/hexchat/addons or ~/.config/xchat/addons

Start Hexchat/xchat and navigate to Window>Plugins and scripts>Load>navigate to location of .pl script and load it.

You will need the hexchat perl plugin installed:                 sudo apt install hexchat-perl

Type /bhelp in hexchat/xchat for list of commands

